com.digitalpersona.uareu

Interface Fmd


  • public interface Fmd
    Class represents Fingerprint Minutiae Data (FMD).

    Class reflects ANSI INSITS 378-2004 and ISO IEC 19794-2-2005 formats.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int getCaptureEquipmentCompliance()
      Returns capture equipment compliance, 4 bits, from "ANSI INSITS 378-2004"
      int getCaptureEquipmentId()
      Returns 12 bits: capture device id, vendor specified
      int getCbeffId()
      Returns CBEFF product identifier
      byte[] getData()
      Returns complete binary data of the FMD, including record header and all views
      Fmd.Format getFormat()
      Returns format of the FMD
      int getHeight()
      Returns height of the fingerprint image, in pixels
      int getResolution()
      Returns resolution of the fingerprint image (pixels per cm for ANSI, pixels per inch for ISO)
      int getViewCnt()
      Returns total number of fingerprints in the record, must be greater or equal to 1
      Fmd.Fmv[] getViews()
      Returns views of the FMD
      int getWidth()
      Returns width of the fingerprint image, in pixels
